---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-white border-t border-gray-200 mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <!-- 로고 + 설명 -->
      <div class="text-center md:text-left">
        <a href="/" class="font-bold text-primary-700 text-lg hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">
          mycalcstool
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">
          실생활에 유용한 무료 온라인 계산기 모음
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 링크 -->
      <nav class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm" aria-label="푸터 링크">
        <a href="/about" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">사이트 소개</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">개인정보처리방침</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">이용약관</a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100">
      <p class="text-center text-xs text-gray-400">
        © {currentYear} mycalcstool. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <p class="text-center text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">
        본 계산기는 참고용이며 법적 효력이 없습니다. 중요한 금융·세무·의료 결정은 전문가와 상담하세요.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
